    dc:description "Fig. 4. Distribution of Drypetes gabonensis Pierre ex Hutch. (blue circles), Drypetes aphanes Quintanar, D.J.Harris & Barberá sp. nov. (red triangles) and D.cauta D.J.Harris, Barberá & Quintanar sp. nov. (green squares)." ;
